---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Privacy Policy - Campus Witches" currentLang="en">
  <div class="max-w-3xl py-12">
    <h1 class="app-h1 mb-6 text-4xl font-black text-purple-600">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-6">
      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          Campus Witches values your privacy. This policy explains what data we collect and how we use it.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600">2. Data We Collect</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-700">We may collect:</p>
        <ul class="ml-4 list-inside list-disc space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>Name and email address</li>
          <li>Browser and device details</li>
          <li>Page visits and interaction metrics</li>
          <li>Information submitted through forms</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600">3. How We Use Data</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-700">Collected data is used to:</p>
        <ul class="ml-4 list-inside list-disc space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>Provide updates and notices</li>
          <li>Manage event and content workflows</li>
          <li>Improve site performance</li>
          <li>Respond to communication requests</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600">4. Data Security</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          We use technical and administrative measures to protect data. Access is limited to authorized roles.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600">5. Cookies</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          Cookies may be used to improve the website experience. You can manage cookie preferences in your browser.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600">6. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          The site may rely on external technical service providers. Please review their own privacy policies.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600">7. Contact</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          For questions, contact us at
          <a href="mailto:kampuscadilari8@gmail.com" class="text-purple-600 hover:underline">kampuscadilari8@gmail.com</a>
          or through the community's official social media accounts.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
